Leonard Strong (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leonard_Strong_(actor) 0 Leonard Clarence Strong (born August 12, 1908, Salt Lake City, Utah – January 23, 1980, Glendale, California) was an American character actor specializing in playing Asian roles.
